snippet.title: Michael | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
MICHAEL - in cinemas soon.
____ 
Michael is the cinematic portrayal of the life and legacy of one of the most influential artists the world has ever known.
 
The film tells the story of Michael Jackson‚Äôs life beyond the music, tracing his journey from the discovery of his extraordinary talent as the lead of the Jackson Five, to the visionary artist whose creative ambition fueled a relentless pursuit to become the biggest entertainer in the world.
 
Highlighting both his life off-stage and some of the most iconic performances from his early solo career, the film gives audiences a front-row seat to Michael Jackson as never before. This is where his story begins.
 
Michael stars Jaafar Jackson in his feature film debut, Nia Long (Empire, The Best Man franchise), Laura Harrier (BlacKkKlansman, Spider-Man: Homecoming) and Juliano Krue Valdi (The Loud House, Arco), with Miles Teller (Top Gun: Maverick, Whiplash) and two-time Academy Award¬Æ nominee Colman Domingo (Sing Sing, Rustin).
 
Directed by Antoine Fuqua, the award-winning filmmaker of Training Day, Olympus Has Fallen and The Equalizer franchise, from a screenplay by three-time Academy Award¬Æ nominee John Logan (Gladiator, The Aviator), the film is produced by Academy Award¬Æ winner Graham King (The Departed, Bohemian Rhapsody), John Branca (executive producer This Is It, Thriller 40) and John McClain (executive producer This Is It, Michael Jackson Live at Wembley July 16, 1988).

snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: 500 Worlds - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Demetrian Titus: officer, leader, strategist. Once again, Captain of the Ultramarines Second Company, Titus faces a new mission with impossible odds ‚Äì but he's not alone!

The 500 Worlds of Ultramar have been slowly gnawed away for millennia, but no more ‚Äì Roboute Guilliman has decreed that they must be retaken, and the newly (re)ordained Captain Titus is at the forefront. In their way: the living metal personification of the mind-snapping destroyer virus, Nekrosor Ammentar, whose rampage has already silenced scores of worlds.

Quentin Tarantino‚Äôs KILL BILL: THE WHOLE BLOODY AFFAIR unites Volume 1 and Volume 2 into a single, unrated epic‚Äîpresented exactly as he intended, complete with a new, never-before-seen anime sequence. Uma Thurman stars as The Bride, left for dead after her former boss and lover Bill ambushes her wedding rehearsal, shooting her in the head and stealing her unborn child. To exact her vengeance, she must first hunt down the four remaining members of the Deadly Viper Assassination Squad before confronting Bill himself. With its operatic scope, relentless action, and iconic style, THE WHOLE BLOODY AFFAIR stands as one of cinema‚Äôs definitive revenge sagas‚Äîrarely shown in its complete form, and now presented with a classic intermission.

snippet.title: Wicked: For Good | Witness the Epic Conclusion
snippet.description:
Every decision has led to this epic conclusion.

Pre-order Wicked: For Good - The Soundtrack üíöü©∑ available November 21st at https://wickedthesoundtrack.lnk.to/forgood
-----
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@wickedmovie
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/wickedmovie
X: https://twitter.com/wickedmovie
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/wickedmovie
Official Site: https://wickedmovie.com

And now whatever way our stories end, I know you have rewritten mine by being my friend ‚Ä¶

Last year‚Äôs global cinematic cultural sensation, which became the most successful Broadway film adaptation of all time, now reaches its epic, electrifying, emotional conclusion in Wicked: For Good. 

Directed once again by award-winning director Jon M. Chu and starring the spectacular returning cast, led by Academy Award¬Æ nominated superstars Cynthia Erivo and Ariana Grande, the final chapter of the untold story of the witches of Oz begins with Elphaba and Glinda estranged and living with the consequences of their choices. 

Elphaba (Cynthia Erivo), now demonized as The Wicked Witch of the West, lives in exile, hidden within the Ozian forest while continuing her fight for the freedom of Oz‚Äôs silenced Animals and desperately trying to expose the truth she knows about The Wizard (Jeff Goldblum).  

Glinda, meanwhile, has become the glamorous symbol of Goodness for all of Oz, living at the palace in Emerald City and reveling in the perks of fame and popularity. Under the instruction of Madame Morrible (Oscar¬Æ winner Michelle Yeoh), Glinda is deployed to serve as an effervescent comfort to Oz, reassuring the masses that all is well under the rule of The Wizard.  

As Glinda‚Äôs stardom expands and she prepares to marry Prince Fiyero (Olivier award winner and Emmy and SAG nominee Jonathan Bailey) in a spectacular Ozian wedding, she is haunted by her separation from Elphaba. She attempts to broker a conciliation between Elphaba and The Wizard, but those efforts will fail, driving Elphaba and Glinda only further apart. The aftershocks will transform Boq (Tony nominee Ethan Slater) and Fiyero forever, and threaten the safety of Elphaba‚Äôs sister, Nessarose (Marissa Bode), when a girl from Kansas comes crashing into all their lives. 

As an angry mob rises against the Wicked Witch, Glinda and Elphaba will need to come together one final time. With their singular friendship now the fulcrum of their futures, they will need to truly see each other, with honesty and empathy, if they are to change themselves, and all of Oz, for good. 

Wicked: For Good also stars Emmy nominee Bowen Yang and Bronwyn James as Glinda‚Äôs fawning assistants, Pfannee and ShenShen and BAFTA and Grammy nominee Sharon D. Clarke (Caroline, or Change) as the voice of Elphaba‚Äôs childhood nanny, Dulcibear. 

The film is produced by returning Tony and Emmy winning powerhouse Marc Platt p.g.a. and by multiple Tony winner David Stone. The executive producers are Stephen Schwartz, David Nicksay, Jared LeBoff, Winnie Holzman and Dana Fox. The first film, Wicked, released in November 2024, earned 10 Academy Award¬Æ nominations, including Best Picture, and won the Oscars¬Æ for Costume Design and Production Design. To date, the film has grossed $750 million worldwide. 

Wicked: For Good is based on the generation-defining musical stage play with music and lyrics by legendary Grammy and Oscar¬Æ winning composer and lyricist Stephen Schwartz and book by Winnie Holzman, from the bestselling novel by Gregory Maguire. The screenplay is by Winnie Holzman and Winnie Holzman & Dana Fox. The film score is by John Powell & Stephen Schwartz, with music and lyrics by Stephen Schwartz.

it.description:
Ogni decisione ha portato a questa conclusione epica.

E ora, qualunque sia il finale delle nostre storie, so che hai riscritto la mia essendo mio amico...

Il successo cinematografico mondiale dell'anno scorso, che √® diventato l'adattamento cinematografico di Broadway di maggior successo di tutti i tempi, raggiunge ora la sua conclusione epica, elettrizzante ed emozionante in Wicked: For Good.

Diretto ancora una volta dal pluripremiato regista Jon M. Chu e interpretato dallo spettacolare cast di ritorno, guidato dalle superstar candidate all'Oscar¬Æ Cynthia Erivo e Ariana Grande, il capitolo finale della storia inedita delle streghe di Oz inizia con Elphaba e Glinda separate e costrette a convivere con le conseguenze delle loro scelte.

Elphaba (Cynthia Erivo), ora demonizzata come la Strega Cattiva dell'Ovest, vive in esilio, nascosta nella foresta di Oz, mentre continua la sua lotta per la libert√† degli Animali di Oz ridotti al silenzio e cerca disperatamente di svelare la verit√† che conosce sul Mago (Jeff Goldblum).

Glinda, nel frattempo, √® diventata il simbolo glamour della Bont√† per tutta Oz, vivendo nel palazzo di Emerald City e godendosi i vantaggi della fama e della popolarit√†. Sotto la guida di Madame Morrible (la vincitrice dell'Oscar¬Æ Michelle Yeoh), Glinda viene inviata a fungere da effervescente conforto a Oz, rassicurando le masse che tutto va bene sotto il dominio del Mago.

Mentre la celebrit√† di Glinda si espande e si prepara a sposare il Principe Fiyero (Jonathan Bailey, vincitore del premio Olivier e candidato agli Emmy e ai SAG) in uno spettacolare matrimonio di Oz, √® tormentata dalla sua separazione da Elphaba. Tenta di mediare una conciliazione tra Elphaba e il Mago, ma i suoi sforzi falliranno, allontanando ulteriormente Elphaba e Glinda. Le scosse di assestamento trasformeranno per sempre Boq (Ethan Slater, candidato ai Tony) e Fiyero, e minacceranno la sicurezza della sorella di Elphaba, Nessarose (Marissa Bode), quando una ragazza del Kansas irromper√† nelle loro vite.

Mentre una folla inferocita si ribella alla Strega Cattiva, Glinda ed Elphaba dovranno unirsi un'ultima volta. Con la loro singolare amicizia ora al centro del loro futuro, dovranno vedersi davvero, con onest√† ed empatia, se vogliono cambiare se stessi e tutto Oz, per sempre.

Wicked: For Good vede anche la partecipazione dei candidati agli Emmy Bowen Yang e Bronwyn James nei panni degli adulatori assistenti di Glinda, Pfannee e ShenShen, e della candidata ai BAFTA e ai Grammy Sharon D. Clarke (Caroline, o Change) nel ruolo della tata d'infanzia di Elphaba, Dulcibear.

Il film √® prodotto dal pluripremiato Marc Platt p.g.a., vincitore di un Tony Award e di un Emmy Award, e dal pluripremiato David Stone. I produttori esecutivi sono Stephen Schwartz, David Nicksay, Jared LeBoff, Winnie Holzman e Dana Fox. Il primo film, Wicked, uscito nel novembre 2024, ha ottenuto 10 nomination agli Oscar¬Æ, tra cui Miglior Film, e ha vinto gli Oscar¬Æ per i Costumi e la Scenografia. Ad oggi, il film ha incassato 750 milioni di dollari in tutto il mondo.

Wicked: For Good √® basato sull'omonimo musical teatrale che ha segnato una generazione, con musiche e testi del leggendario compositore e paroliere vincitore di un Grammy e di un Oscar¬Æ, Stephen Schwartz, e sul libretto di Winnie Holzman, tratto dal romanzo bestseller di Gregory Maguire. La sceneggiatura √® di Winnie Holzman e Winnie Holzman e Dana Fox. La colonna sonora √® di John Powell e Stephen Schwartz, con musiche e testi di Stephen Schwartz.

And now whatever way our stories end, I know you have rewritten mine by being my friend ‚Ä¶

Last year‚Äôs global cinematic cultural sensation, which became the most successful Broadway film adaptation of all time, now reaches its epic, electrifying, emotional conclusion in Wicked: For Good. 

Directed once again by award-winning director Jon M. Chu and starring the spectacular returning cast, led by Academy Award¬Æ nominated superstars Cynthia Erivo and Ariana Grande, the final chapter of the untold story of the witches of Oz begins with Elphaba and Glinda estranged and living with the consequences of their choices. 

Elphaba (Cynthia Erivo), now demonized as The Wicked Witch of the West, lives in exile, hidden within the Ozian forest while continuing her fight for the freedom of Oz‚Äôs silenced Animals and desperately trying to expose the truth she knows about The Wizard (Jeff Goldblum).  

Glinda, meanwhile, has become the glamorous symbol of Goodness for all of Oz, living at the palace in Emerald City and reveling in the perks of fame and popularity. Under the instruction of Madame Morrible (Oscar¬Æ winner Michelle Yeoh), Glinda is deployed to serve as an effervescent comfort to Oz, reassuring the masses that all is well under the rule of The Wizard.  

As Glinda‚Äôs stardom expands and she prepares to marry Prince Fiyero (Olivier award winner and Emmy and SAG nominee Jonathan Bailey) in a spectacular Ozian wedding, she is haunted by her separation from Elphaba. She attempts to broker a conciliation between Elphaba and The Wizard, but those efforts will fail, driving Elphaba and Glinda only further apart. The aftershocks will transform Boq (Tony nominee Ethan Slater) and Fiyero forever, and threaten the safety of Elphaba‚Äôs sister, Nessarose (Marissa Bode), when a girl from Kansas comes crashing into all their lives. 

As an angry mob rises against the Wicked Witch, Glinda and Elphaba will need to come together one final time. With their singular friendship now the fulcrum of their futures, they will need to truly see each other, with honesty and empathy, if they are to change themselves, and all of Oz, for good. 

Wicked: For Good also stars Emmy nominee Bowen Yang and Bronwyn James as Glinda‚Äôs fawning assistants, Pfannee and ShenShen and BAFTA and Grammy nominee Sharon D. Clarke (Caroline, or Change) as the voice of Elphaba‚Äôs childhood nanny, Dulcibear. 

The film is produced by returning Tony and Emmy winning powerhouse Marc Platt p.g.a. and by multiple Tony winner David Stone. The executive producers are Stephen Schwartz, David Nicksay, Jared LeBoff, Winnie Holzman and Dana Fox. The first film, Wicked, released in November 2024, earned 10 Academy Award¬Æ nominations, including Best Picture, and won the Oscars¬Æ for Costume Design and Production Design. To date, the film has grossed $750 million worldwide. 

Wicked: For Good is based on the generation-defining musical stage play with music and lyrics by legendary Grammy and Oscar¬Æ winning composer and lyricist Stephen Schwartz and book by Winnie Holzman, from the bestselling novel by Gregory Maguire. The screenplay is by Winnie Holzman and Winnie Holzman & Dana Fox. The film score is by John Powell & Stephen Schwartz, with music and lyrics by Stephen Schwartz.

Dan kini, apa pun akhir kisah kita, aku tahu kau telah menulis ulang kisahku dengan menjadi temanku...

Sensasi budaya sinematik global tahun lalu, yang menjadi adaptasi film Broadway tersukses sepanjang masa, kini mencapai akhir yang epik, menggetarkan, dan emosional dalam Wicked: For Good.

Disutradarai kembali oleh sutradara peraih penghargaan Jon M. Chu dan dibintangi oleh para pemeran kembali yang spektakuler, dipimpin oleh superstar nominasi Academy Award¬Æ Cynthia Erivo dan Ariana Grande, bab terakhir dari kisah para penyihir Oz yang tak terungkap dimulai dengan Elphaba dan Glinda yang terasing dan hidup dengan konsekuensi dari pilihan mereka.

Elphaba (Cynthia Erivo), yang kini disetankan sebagai Penyihir Jahat dari Barat, hidup dalam pengasingan, tersembunyi di dalam hutan Ozian sambil melanjutkan perjuangannya untuk kebebasan Hewan-hewan Oz yang dibungkam dan mati-matian berusaha mengungkap kebenaran yang diketahuinya tentang Sang Penyihir (Jeff Goldblum).

Sementara itu, Glinda telah menjadi simbol Kebaikan yang glamor bagi seluruh Oz, tinggal di istana di Emerald City dan menikmati keuntungan dari ketenaran dan popularitas. Di bawah instruksi Madame Morrible (pemenang Oscar¬Æ Michelle Yeoh), Glinda dikerahkan untuk menjadi penghibur Oz yang bersemangat, meyakinkan masyarakat bahwa semuanya baik-baik saja di bawah kekuasaan Sang Penyihir.

Seiring ketenaran Glinda melejit dan ia bersiap menikahi Pangeran Fiyero (pemenang penghargaan Olivier dan nominasi Emmy dan SAG Jonathan Bailey) dalam pernikahan spektakuler di Ozian, ia dihantui oleh perpisahannya dengan Elphaba. Ia mencoba mendamaikan Elphaba dan Sang Penyihir, tetapi upaya tersebut gagal, membuat Elphaba dan Glinda semakin menjauh. Gempa susulan akan mengubah Boq (nominasi Tony Ethan Slater) dan Fiyero selamanya, dan mengancam keselamatan saudara perempuan Elphaba, Nessarose (Marissa Bode), ketika seorang gadis dari Kansas datang menerjang kehidupan mereka.

Saat massa yang marah bangkit melawan Penyihir Jahat, Glinda dan Elphaba harus bersatu untuk terakhir kalinya. Dengan persahabatan mereka yang kini menjadi tumpuan masa depan mereka, mereka perlu benar-benar melihat satu sama lain, dengan kejujuran dan empati, jika mereka ingin mengubah diri mereka sendiri, dan seluruh Oz, untuk selamanya.

Wicked: For Good juga dibintangi oleh nominasi Emmy, Bowen Yang dan Bronwyn James, sebagai asisten Glinda yang selalu memuja, Pfannee dan ShenShen, serta nominasi BAFTA dan Grammy, Sharon D. Clarke (Caroline, atau Change), sebagai pengisi suara pengasuh masa kecil Elphaba, Dulcibear.

Film ini diproduksi oleh Marc Platt, peraih Tony dan Emmy yang kembali, dan David Stone, peraih beberapa penghargaan Tony. Produser eksekutifnya adalah Stephen Schwartz, David Nicksay, Jared LeBoff, Winnie Holzman, dan Dana Fox. Film pertamanya, Wicked, yang dirilis pada November 2024, meraih 10 nominasi Academy Award¬Æ, termasuk Film Terbaik, dan memenangkan Oscar¬Æ untuk Desain Kostum dan Desain Produksi. Hingga saat ini, film ini telah meraup pendapatan kotor sebesar $750 juta di seluruh dunia.

Wicked: For Good diadaptasi dari drama panggung musikal yang menjadi ikon generasi ini, dengan musik dan lirik karya komposer sekaligus penulis lirik legendaris peraih Grammy dan Oscar¬Æ, Stephen Schwartz, dan buku karya Winnie Holzman, yang diadaptasi dari novel terlaris karya Gregory Maguire. Skenarionya ditulis oleh Winnie Holzman dan Winnie Holzman & Dana Fox. Musik latar filmnya ditulis oleh John Powell & Stephen Schwartz, dengan musik dan lirik oleh Stephen Schwartz.

snippet.description:
The Fray - How To Save A Life (Lyrics): 

‚≠êFollow Dead Radio Club:
Instagram:  https://www.instagram.com/davcev/?hl=en
Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/playlist/0xF5l1EUXHQUG8jryaJrfN?si=bee0d3552a124b39
üî¥ Picture : https://lexica.art/ 

‚≠êThe Fray:
Facebook: https://TheFray.lnk.to/followFI‚Äã

Site: https://TheFray.lnk.to/followWI
Instagram: https://TheFray.lnk.to/followII
Youtube: https://TheFray.lnk.to/subscribeYD:

Lyrics:

Step one, you say, "We need to talk"
He walks, you say, "Sit down, it's just a talk"
He smiles politely back at you
You stare politely right on through
Some sort of window to your right
As he goes left and you stay right
Between the lines of fear and blame
You begin to wonder why you came
Where did I go wrong? I lost a friend
Somewhere along in the bitterness
And I would have stayed up with you all night
Had I known how to save a life
Let him know that you know best
'Cause after all, you do know best
You try to slip past his defense
Without granting innocence
Lay down a list of what is wrong
The things you've told him all along
Pray to God he hears you
And pray to God he hears you
And where did I go wrong? I lost a friend
Somewhere along in the bitterness
And I would have stayed up with you all night
Had I known how to save a life
As he begins to raise his voice
You lower yours and grant him one last choice
Drive until you lose the road
Or break with the ones you've followed
He will do one of two things
He will admit to everything
Or he'll say he's just not the same
And you'll begin to wonder why you came
Where did I go wrong? I lost a friend
Somewhere along in the bitterness
And I would have stayed up with you all night
Had I known how to save a life

Somewhere along in the bitterness
And I would have stayed up with you all night
Had I known how to save a life

And I would have stayed up with you all night
Had I known how to save a life

And I would have stayed up with you all night (and I would have stayed up)

Lyrics:
Hey, how you doing? How's your day going?
You know that you can always say what's on your mind
Are you on your way home?
I'll warm up yo plate when you arrive
Hang yo coat, take off ya shoes, hot water in the tub for you
Don't have to, but I love to do
Bartender, I'll pour a drink, a movie on to entertain
I'm down to do the little things

Just wanna take some time to thank ya
And let you know just how you make me proud
The good times make up for the bad ones
I see you trying, and I don't know how
You keep up with me when ya working
Switch ya timing when our schedules aren't aligning
That's a sign, that's a sign
That it's okay to finally tell the world that you are more than enough, –µnough, enough
For me

Be right h–µre when you waking up
Breakfast on the table, know you like
Eggs and they're all scrambled up
Pancakes, bacon, OJ on the side
Packed your bag with extra clothes, yo toothbrush in the Louis tote
Love notes for when you on the road (Yeah, yeah, yeah)
Cleaned yo watch and Cuban links
Silk pillowcase for you to take
Boy, you deserve the little things, yeah, yeah

Just wanna take some time to thank ya
And let you know just how you make me proud
The good times make up for the bad ones
I see you trying, and I don't know how
You keep up with me when ya working
Switch ya timing when our schedules aren't aligning
That's a sign, that's a sign
That it's okay to finally tell the world that you are more than enough, enough, enough
For me

More than I can say
And you keep giving me more and more each day
Oh, baby, and I never thought I'd end up with
The man of my dreams, you really him
I don't mind taking time, baby, I'm down to do the little things
More than I can say
And you keep giving me more and more each day
Oh, baby, and I never thought I'd end up with
The man of my dreams, you really him
I don't mind taking time, baby, I'm down to do the little things

I'm down to do the little things
I'm down to do the little things (Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah)
Yeah, yeah, I don't mind taking time
Baby, I'm down to do the little things

snippet.title: The Family Man S3 - Official Trailer | Raj & DK | Manoj Bajpayee, Jaideep Ahlawat | Prime Video IN
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
The Family Man Season 3 Official Trailer 

SERIES:
"The Family Man," created by Raj & DK, an edgy and thrilling series on Prime Video, follows the life of Srikant Tiwari, a seemingly ordinary middle-class man who secretly works for the Threat Assessment and Surveillance Cell( TASC), a fictional cell of the National Investigation Agency in Mumbai. Balancing the demands of his high-stakes job and his family, life proves increasingly challenging as Srikant navigates dangerous missions against terrorists while trying to be a present husband and father. As he dives deeper into the murky world of espionage, Srikant must protect his loved ones from the perils of his covert profession, all while grappling with moral dilemmas that test his integrity and loyalty.

SEASON:
Outlawed and on the run, Srikant Tiwari faces sinister forces threatening to ignite chaos in Northeast India, uncovering a conspiracy that could plunge the nation into war.

Created by: Raj & DK

Directed by: Raj & DK, Suman Kumar, Tusshar Seyth
Produced by: Raj & DK
Written by Suman Kumar, Raj & DK
Screenplays by: Suman Kumar, Raj & DK, Sudhish Kamath, Nikhil Gonsalves  
Dialogues: Sumit Arora

Associate Producer: Anuradha Sharma
Executive Producer: Vikesh Bhutani, Ankita Batra
Associate Director: Chesta Goswami

Director Of Photography: Jay Charola
Production Designer: Parichit Paralkar
Editor: Sumeet Kotian
Post-Production Producer: Jespal Nadar
Action Directors: Yannick Ben Haddou, Aejaz Gulab
Sound Design: Sanjay Maurya & Allwin Rego
Background Score: Ketan Sodha 
Costume Designer: Neha. R. Bajaj
Casting Director: Mukesh Chhabra CSA 

First Assistant Director: Durgesh Pratap Singh 
Additional Writing: Suhas Navarathna
Production Supervisor: Utkarsha Kohli 
Special Advisor: Bimal Parekh

A D2R Films Production

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages ‚Äì including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal ‚Äì The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video‚Äôs video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures ‚Äì Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

snippet.title: Minecraft But There's K-POP DEMON HUNTER Hearts
snippet.description:
This is Minecraft But There's K-POP DEMON HUNTER Hearts! When Steve's hearts get stolen by the K-POP DEMON HUNTERS such as Rumi, Mira, Bobby, Jinu, Zoey, Derpy, Sussie he needs to defeat the K-POP DEMON HUNTER characters! Steve needs to learn how to be and behave like a real K-POP DEMON HUNTER character if he wants to use all the new K-POP DEMON HUNTER powers, gadgets, and abilities! Can Steve learn all the secrets and abilities of K-POP DEMON HUNTER, get all the K-POP DEMON HUNTER, and upgrade into the ultimate K-POP DEMON HUNTER? This is Minecraft But There's K-POP DEMON HUNTER Hearts!
__

üßëüèº‚Äçü§ù‚Äçüßëüèº Join the Community on Discord: https://discord.gg/jkfV7mSxB6

MORE CHECKPOINT ADVENTURES:

‚Ä£ MINECRAFT DIMENSION: https://bit.ly/3mKfUOL


¬¨

Minecraft is an open world game that has no specific goals for the player to accomplish, allowing players a large amount of freedom in choosing how to play the game however, there is an achievement system. The gameplay by default is first person, but players have the option to play in third person mode. The core gameplay revolves around breaking and placing blocks. The game world is essentially composed of rough 3D objects‚Äîmainly cubes‚Äîthat are arranged in a fixed grid pattern and represent different materials, such as dirt, stone, various ores, water, and tree trunks. While players can move freely across the world, objects and items can only be placed at fixed locations relative to the grid. Players can gather these material blocks and place them elsewhere, thus allowing for various constructions.

#Checkpoint #Minecraft

snippet.description:
‚Ä¢ESCUCHA AQU√ç ‚ÄúEspejo‚Äù
https://www.doublepmusic.com/espejo

‚Ä¢LETRA
Me miro en el espejo y en caliente da el reflejo que me parezco un chingo a mi ap√° s√© que
tengo un car√°cter de la chingada pero yo solamente me doy a respetar

Entre m√°s avanzo
me doy cuenta
de qu√© estoy rodeado
de la envidia de sonrisas falsas
Y no es que quieran
lo que tengo
quieren que yo no lo tenga
y eso les arde la panza

Se donde estoy y pa donde voy
En quien conf√≠o solamente en Dios

Me miro en el espejo y en caliente da el reflejo que me parezco un chingo a mi ap√° s√© que
tengo un car√°cter de la chingada pero yo solamente me doy a respetar

Traigo en la lista
Al envidioso al doble cara
Al ego√≠sta al mentiroso
Al traicionero
Al mitotero al falso amigo que te busca por dinero

Las traiciones me ense√±aron lo que es un libro no te dice
por eso mi cuerpo tiene un chingo e cicatrices
Mi am√° me dec√≠a nunca metas las narices donde no te llaman

Me echo un kratom y prendo un tabaco
Pa lo ondeado yo me chingo un trago
Tinto el vino pa andar tranquilino con
un suspiro de Danonino

Las 4 de la mara√±a me levanto de la cama sin poder dormir me pongo a forjar sigo pensando
puras babosadas pero si le pones mente es la pura verdad

En donde estoy pa donde voy
En quien conf√≠o solamente en Dios

Me sobran los motivos pa‚Äô decir lo que digo checamos el archivo est√° lleno de negativos

Tengo motivos por eso lo digo no ocupo testigos ni malos amigos que busquen sonido

snippet.title: My Starter Base Is ALIVE! -  Hermitcraft 11 Episode 1
snippet.description:
Use code SCARFB50 to get 50% OFF your first Factor box plus free breakfast for 1 year at https://bit.ly/3IWcXd  *AD

Welcome to Hermitcraft Season 11 ‚Äî Episode 1!
We‚Äôre starting off with a big Minecraft challenge: creating a massive, organic alien creature using only copper tools. My Hermitcraft smp starter base this season is actually the creature itself ‚Äî something I ride across the alien planet I crash-landed on long ago after the rebellion.

This season‚Äôs base theme is fantasy-in-space: a sprawling spaceport and a massive redstone game project. The main base will be called Scar Worlds: The Movie.

In Episode 1, we also hang out with Grian, Mumbo, and Gem. We escape the Nether after mysteriously spawning there, and then go on some hilarious mining and caving adventures together.

I really hope you like the base story and ideas! See you in episode 2!

snippet.title: Hilary Duff - Mature (Official Video)
snippet.description:
"Mature" out now: https://hilaryduff.lnk.to/Mature

Lyrics: 

[Verse 1]
She's me, I'm her in a different font
Just a few years younger, a new haircut
Very Leo of you with your Scorpio touch
Now, now
Going down on her on your vintage rug
Bet she's so impressed by your Basquiat
And she thinks you're deep in the ways you're not
Now, now

[Pre-Chorus]
I can't put it on her, she's a sweet kid
But she's taking the bait like we all did

[Chorus]
She looks
Like all of your girls but blonder
A little like me, just younger
Bet she loves when she hears you say
"You're so mature for your age, babe"
She looks
Like she could be your daughter
Like me before I got smarter
When I was flattered to hear you say
"You're so mature for your age, babe," oh

[Verse 2]
You dim all the lights so you look real wise
As they trace the lines underneath your eyes
And mistake your charm for a cosmic sign
Now, now

[Pre-Chorus]
I can't put it on them, it's his best trick
And they're taking the bait just like I did

[Chorus]
She looks
Like all of your girls but blonder
A little like me, just younger
Bet she loves when she hears you say
"You're so mature for your age, babe"
She looks
Like she could be your daughter
Like me before I got smarter
When I was flattered to hear you say
"You're so mature for your age, babe"

[Post-Chorus]
Watched the tide rise up as high as you got on me
Listening to Strawberry Letter 23
Hid my car at Carbon Beach so I wasn't seen at yours
You knew better of course

[Bridge]
Oh, you're so mature
You're so mature
Oh

[Chorus]
She looks
Like all of your girls but blonder
A little like me, just younger
Bet she loves when she hears you say
"You're so mature for your age, babe"
She looks (She looks)
Like she could be your daughter
Like me before I got smarter
When I was flattered to hear you say
"You're so mature for your age, babe"

[Post-Chorus]
Watched the tide rise up as high as you got on me
Listening to Strawberry Letter 23
Hid my car at Carbon Beach so I wasn't seen at yours
You're so mature for your age, babe

The official Legendary Lyric video for Born on the Bayou by Creedence Clearwater Revival, from their 1969 album Bayou Country.

https://ccr.concord.com/products/

Subscribe to the CCR Newsletter: https://manage.kmail-lists.com/subscriptions/subscribe?a=Ut6Y6V&g=WyE6eZ

About Creedence Clearwater Revival: 
Creedence Clearwater Revival‚Äôs 1968 self-titled debut album introduced the world to guitar-playing brothers John and Tom‚ÄØFogerty, drummer Doug Clifford, and bassist Stu Cook, four young men out of El Cerrito in the San Francisco Bay Area. Though they emerged in a place and time where trippy psychedelic visions were the order of‚ÄØthe day, CCR bucked the trends and instead tapped into a rich, traditional seam of American music that connected to blues, country, rockabilly, gospel, folk and R&B.‚ÄØ‚ÄØ‚ÄØ 

During their short time together as a band (1968 ‚Äì 1972), the band enjoyed an unparalleled period of creativity lead by singer, songwriter, arranger John Fogerty. They‚Äôve sold close to 100 million records, releasing 14 Top 10 hits. They also managed to play over 150 tour dates around the world, including a headlining spot at Woodstock.

Creedence Clearwater Revival‚Äôs canon has become a part of the Great American Songbook. Fogerty penned songs like ‚ÄúBad Moon Rising,‚Äù ‚ÄúDown on the Corner,‚Äù ‚ÄúFortunate Son,‚Äù ‚ÄúHave You Ever Seen the Rain,‚Äù ‚ÄúProud Mary,‚Äù ‚ÄúBorn on the Bayou,‚Äù ‚ÄúTravelin‚Äô Band‚Äù and ‚ÄúUp Around the Bend‚Äù have been ingrained into pop culture ‚Äî not just as rock staples, but as classic standards.

With so many memorable songs that continue to grace our radio waves, television and movie screens, plus lyrics that still resonate today, Creedence Clearwater Revival is, truly, America‚Äôs greatest rock ‚Äôn‚Äô roll band.

snippet.title: Cody Johnson - Travelin' Soldier (Studio Visualizer)
snippet.description:
Cody Johnson - Travelin' Soldier (Studio Visualizer)

Listen to the 'Leather' Deluxe album: https://codyjohnson.lnk.to/leatherdeluxe

Subscribe to Cody's channel for all the latest: https://bit.ly/2D9PWQo

Follow Cody on socials! 
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/CodyJohnsonBand
Instagram: https://CodyJohnson.lnk.to/instagram 
Facebook: https://CodyJohnson.lnk.to/facebook
Website: https://www.codyjohnsonmusic.com
Spotify: https://CodyJohnson.lnk.to/spotify

The official YouTube channel of Cody Johnson.
 
Cody Johnson has established a following of passionately loyal fans who regularly sell out shows across the country. The artist that media has touted ‚Äújust might be the future of real country music‚Äù has skyrocketed success with numerous celebrated albums: Leather Deluxe Edition, Leather, Human The Double Album, A Cody Johnson Christmas, Cody Johnson & The Rockin‚Äô CJB Live, and Ain‚Äôt Nothin‚Äô To It plus an award-winning feature-length documentary ‚ÄúDear Rodeo: The Cody Johnson Story.‚Äù Cody has 42 Gold and Platinum certifications, nearly 10 Billion career global streams and four #1 singles. 
 
Cody‚Äôs #1 single ‚ÄúDirt Cheap,‚Äù written by Josh Philips, was awarded as Storyteller of The Year at the ‚ÄúPeople‚Äôs Choice Country Awards‚Äù and ‚ÄúThe Painter‚Äù was awarded as the NSAI 2024 Song of The Year for writers Benjy Davis, Kat Higgins and Ryan Larkins. Both #1 hits are included on Cody‚Äôs current album Leather Deluxe Edition.  
 
His numerous industry honors include recognition as a CMT Artist of The Year, two ACM Awards, three CMT Music Awards wins, four CMA Awards including Album of The Year (2024) for Leather, and being named ‚ÄúBest New Country Artist‚Äù at the iHeart Music and recognized with the Spirit award at the 2025 ACM Honors event. His television appearances have entertained fans on the Today Show, the Kelly Clarkson Show and the Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon in addition to outstanding live tv performances at the iHeart Music Awards, the ACM Awards, CMA Awards, CMT Music Awards, CMT Giants honoring Vince Gill, and the CMT Artist of the Year Special and more. Cody co-hosted the three-hour ‚ÄúCMA Fest Presented by Sofi‚Äù with Ashley McBryde this summer.

¬© 2025 CoJo Music / 2025 Warner Music Nashville LLC

#CodyJohnson #TravelinSoldier #CountryMusic

snippet.title: Give A Rest by RecD - Catnap & Smiling Critters Poppy Playtime Fan Song ("Take A Rest" Prequel)
snippet.description:
It's Catnap's first day with the Smiling Critters. They're all super talented, but all he can do is tell people to go to bed! How will he ever fit in?

Stream/Buy: https://distrokid.com/hyperfollow/recd/give-a-rest
Buy on Bandcamp: https://recorderdude.bandcamp.com/album/give-a-rest
Twittter: https://twitter.com/RecDTRH
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/RecD
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/6PWNwEY

Ever since Take A Rest blew up beyond my wildest dreams and turned into a series, I've wanted to make a prequel to explain how Catnap got the way he is in that video. That idea blossomed into this sweeping epic mini-musical combining catchy bossa nova beats with much, much more!

snippet.title: Veeronica X Guest 666 „ÄéComic Dub„Äè
snippet.description:
Veeronica X Guest 666 „ÄéComic Dub„Äè
üñ§ Honey, please subscribe :3
üîî Turn on notifications so you don't miss new videos!

Artist: Me (Rick)
Reference: koi 567, qemars, saikorin

Voice Actor: Me (Rick)
Voice Actress: Shuzuka

Producer: Saikorin
Twitter(X): https://x.com/Saikorin_
Discord(Not Skype): https://discord.gg/B3kfrVmWBR
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/SaikorinOfficial

Dear viewers, you are greeted by part of the team of professional voice acting for anime, films, comics, manga, manhwa and the rest.

Shuzuka and I moved to Canada when we were children.
We really enjoyed watching anime and cartoons and dreamed of becoming voice actors. Unfortunately, Japan has a very competitive environment among seiyuus. But our voices in English provide translations of anime for different countries, you could hear our voices in a variety of anime.
We are currently providing voice-over services for manga and comics, and hope for your support.

On average, we spend about 14 hours creating one video.
At the stage of coming up with an idea, we already begin to sketch out a script in order to save time. At the same time, we are looking for comic book authors and artists who draw manga. After communicating with them, we come up with a title for the video and sketch out a preview. By this point, we have already spent about 4 hours of our time, because in reality this is a very long and tedious process, but very fun. Sometimes I do it alone, but then it takes me about 6 hours (but this is rare).
Then we assign roles. Usually Shizuka completes the script that we sketched out at the beginning. She constantly watches various tutorials and looks for references so that the original comic has a different meaning. She likes to remake the meaning of the entire story, usually in a humorous way.
At this time, I am redrawing most of the comic, according to the redone script, so that the comic ultimately comes out with a completely different meaning. I also spend a huge part of my time redrawing the clothes on the characters and drawing the environment. While drawing, I have to watch a lot of tutorials of different content, since drawing is a rather complicated task. I need to watch instructional videos on YouTube all the time about storyboarding, how to properly draw clothes, human anatomy (sometimes animals) and lighting, as shadows make the drawing better. You need to look through a lot of references in order to choose an idea for clothing, interior design, and simply shading shadows in certain lighting. I absolutely always have all color combinations open on the second monitor. And while Shizuka is finishing the script, I‚Äôm preparing a thumbnail for the video. At the end I add dialogue from Shizuka's script. This usually takes us about 6-8 hours. I don't know how much I would have done it alone without Shizuka's help (Maybe 16 hours?).
After everything we've done, we start dubbing the remade comic. Since we are professional voice actors and have been doing voice acting for quite a long time, we make few mistakes. When editing a video, we often have to re-voice some lines, as we may make a mistake with the intonation. Next, I edit the visual part of the comic in Sony Vegas Pro 11, and Shizuka searches for music from the YouTube library and creates an audio track in Ableton Live 11. After we combine our efforts into one project, we press the render button. By this time we had already spent between 13 and 15 hours.
After all of the above, you were able to see this video.
Thank you for supporting us, liking and subscribing to the channel :)

This video was created for entertainment and humorous purposes only and is not intended to offend anyone!
All materials on this channel has been edited by Saikorin.
We are not the author of the original, I do not take credit for the materials that were used in this video.
All materials have been significantly modified in accordance with the rules of fair use and added to the general plot of the video.

tips the balance in favor of fair use."

Sony Vegas Pro, Adobe Photoshop, Ableton Live 11

it.description:
Veeronica X Ospite 666 „ÄéComic Dub„Äè
üñ§ Tesoro, iscriviti :3
üîî Attiva le notifiche per non perdere i nuovi video!

Artista: Io (Rick)
Riferimento: koi 567, qemars, saikorin

Doppiatore: Io (Rick)
Doppiatrice: Shuzuka

Produttore: Saikorin
Twitter(X): https://x.com/Saikorin_
Discord(Non Skype): https://discord.gg/B3kfrVmWBR
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/SaikorinOfficial

Cari spettatori, vi diamo il benvenuto da parte del team di doppiatori professionisti per anime, film, fumetti, manga, manhwa e altro.

Io e Shuzuka ci siamo trasferiti in Canada da bambini.
Ci piaceva molto guardare anime e cartoni animati e sognavamo di diventare doppiatori. Purtroppo, il Giappone ha un ambiente molto competitivo tra i doppiatori. Ma le nostre voci in inglese forniscono traduzioni di anime per diversi paesi, quindi potete sentire le nostre voci in una variet√† di anime.
Attualmente forniamo servizi di doppiaggio per manga e fumetti e confidiamo nel vostro supporto.

In media, impieghiamo circa 14 ore per creare un video.
Nella fase di ideazione, iniziamo gi√† a delineare una sceneggiatura per risparmiare tempo. Allo stesso tempo, cerchiamo autori e disegnatori di fumetti che disegnino manga. Dopo aver parlato con loro, troviamo un titolo per il video e ne abbozziamo un'anteprima. A questo punto, abbiamo gi√† dedicato circa 4 ore del nostro tempo, perch√© in realt√† √® un processo molto lungo e noioso, ma molto divertente. A volte lo faccio da sola, ma in quel caso ci metto circa 6 ore (ma √® raro).
Poi assegniamo i ruoli. Di solito Shizuka completa la sceneggiatura che abbiamo abbozzato all'inizio. Guarda costantemente vari tutorial e cerca riferimenti in modo che il fumetto originale abbia un significato diverso. Le piace rivisitare il significato dell'intera storia, di solito in modo umoristico.
In questo momento, sto ridisegnando gran parte del fumetto, seguendo la sceneggiatura rielaborata, in modo che il fumetto alla fine abbia un significato completamente diverso. Dedico anche gran parte del mio tempo a ridisegnare gli abiti dei personaggi e a disegnare l'ambiente. Mentre disegno, devo guardare molti tutorial di vario tipo, dato che disegnare √® un compito piuttosto complicato. Devo guardare continuamente video didattici su YouTube sullo storyboard, su come disegnare correttamente i vestiti, sull'anatomia umana (a volte anche quella degli animali) e sull'illuminazione, poich√© le ombre migliorano il disegno. Bisogna consultare molti riferimenti per scegliere un'idea per l'abbigliamento, l'interior design e semplicemente per sfumare le ombre in determinate condizioni di luce. Tengo sempre aperte tutte le combinazioni di colori sul secondo monitor. E mentre Shizuka finisce la sceneggiatura, preparo un'anteprima per il video. Alla fine aggiungo i dialoghi dalla sceneggiatura di Shizuka. Di solito ci vogliono circa 6-8 ore. Non so quanto avrei fatto da sola senza l'aiuto di Shizuka (forse 16 ore?).
Dopo tutto quello che abbiamo fatto, iniziamo a doppiare il fumetto rifatto. Dato che siamo doppiatori professionisti e ci occupiamo di doppiaggio da parecchio tempo, commettiamo pochi errori. Quando modifichiamo un video, spesso dobbiamo rifare alcune battute, perch√© potremmo sbagliare l'intonazione. Poi, modifico la parte visiva del fumetto in Sony Vegas Pro 11, e Shizuka cerca la musica dalla libreria di YouTube e crea una traccia audio in Ableton Live 11. Dopo aver unito i nostri sforzi in un unico progetto, premiamo il pulsante di rendering. A questo punto avevamo gi√† impiegato tra le 13 e le 15 ore.

nl-NL.title: Veeronica X Guest 666 „ÄéComic Dub„Äè
nl-NL.description:
Veeronica X Gast 666 „ÄéComic Dub„Äè
üñ§ Schat, abonneer je alsjeblieft :3
üîî Zet meldingen aan zodat je geen nieuwe video's mist!

Artiest: Ik (Rick)
Referentie: koi 567, qemars, saikorin

Stemacteur: Ik (Rick)
Stemactrice: Shuzuka

Producent: Saikorin
Twitter (X): https://x.com/Saikorin_
Discord (geen Skype): https://discord.gg/B3kfrVmWBR
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/SaikorinOfficial

Beste kijkers, jullie worden begroet door een deel van het team van professionele stemacteurs voor anime, films, strips, manga, manhwa en de rest.

Shuzuka en ik verhuisden naar Canada toen we kinderen waren.
We keken erg graag naar anime en tekenfilms en droomden ervan om stemacteur te worden. Helaas is er in Japan een zeer competitieve omgeving onder seiyuus. Maar onze stemmen in het Engels verzorgen vertalingen van anime voor verschillende landen; je kon onze stemmen in diverse animes horen.
We leveren momenteel voice-overdiensten voor manga en strips en hopen op jouw steun.

Gemiddeld besteden we ongeveer 14 uur aan het maken van √©√©n video.
In de fase van het bedenken van een idee beginnen we al met het schetsen van een script om tijd te besparen. Tegelijkertijd zijn we op zoek naar stripauteurs en tekenaars die manga tekenen. Na overleg met hen bedenken we een titel voor de video en schetsen we een preview. Op dit punt hebben we al ongeveer 4 uur van onze tijd besteed, want in werkelijkheid is dit een heel lang en vervelend proces, maar erg leuk. Soms doe ik het alleen, maar dan kost het me ongeveer 6 uur (maar dat komt zelden voor).
Daarna verdelen we de rollen. Meestal maakt Shizuka het script af dat we in het begin hebben geschetst. Ze bekijkt constant verschillende tutorials en zoekt naar referenties, zodat de originele strip een andere betekenis krijgt. Ze vindt het leuk om de betekenis van het hele verhaal te herschrijven, meestal op een humoristische manier.
Op dit moment teken ik het grootste deel van de strip opnieuw, volgens het vernieuwde script, zodat de strip uiteindelijk een compleet andere betekenis krijgt. Ik besteed ook een groot deel van mijn tijd aan het opnieuw tekenen van de kleding van de personages en het tekenen van de omgeving. Tijdens het tekenen moet ik veel tutorials met verschillende inhoud bekijken, omdat tekenen een vrij ingewikkelde taak is. Ik moet constant instructievideo's op YouTube bekijken over storyboarding, hoe je kleding correct tekent, menselijke anatomie (soms dieren) en belichting, omdat schaduwen de tekening beter maken. Je moet veel referenties bekijken om een ‚Äã‚Äãidee te kiezen voor kleding, interieurontwerp en simpelweg het schaduwen van schaduwen bij bepaalde belichting. Ik heb absoluut altijd alle kleurencombinaties openstaan ‚Äã‚Äãop de tweede monitor. En terwijl Shizuka het script afmaakt, bereid ik een thumbnail voor de video voor. Aan het einde voeg ik dialogen uit Shizuka's script toe. Dit kost ons meestal zo'n 6-8 uur. Ik weet niet hoeveel ik het alleen had gedaan zonder Shizuka's hulp (misschien 16 uur?).
Na alles wat we gedaan hebben, beginnen we met het nasynchroniseren van de nieuwe strip. Omdat we professionele stemacteurs zijn en al geruime tijd voice-acting doen, maken we weinig fouten. Bij het bewerken van een video moeten we vaak wat tekst opnieuw inspreken, omdat we een fout met de intonatie kunnen maken. Vervolgens bewerk ik het visuele gedeelte van de strip in Sony Vegas Pro 11, en Shizuka zoekt muziek in de YouTube-bibliotheek en maakt een audiotrack in Ableton Live 11. Nadat we onze krachten bundelen tot √©√©n project, drukken we op de renderknop. Tegen die tijd hadden we er al tussen de 13 en 15 uur aan besteed.
Na al het bovenstaande heb je deze video kunnen bekijken.
Bedankt voor je steun, je like en je abonnering op het kanaal :)

id.description:
Veeronica X Guest 666 „ÄéComic Dub„Äè
üñ§ Sayang, yuk berlangganan :3
üîî Aktifkan notifikasi agar tidak ketinggalan video baru!

Artis: Saya (Rick)
Referensi: koi 567, qemars, saikorin

Pengisi Suara: Saya (Rick)
Pengisi Suara: Shuzuka

Produser: Saikorin
Twitter (X): https://x.com/Saikorin_
Discord (Bukan Skype): https://discord.gg/B3kfrVmWBR
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/SaikorinOfficial

Para penonton yang terhormat, Anda disambut oleh tim pengisi suara profesional untuk anime, film, komik, manga, manhwa, dan lainnya.

Saya dan Shuzuka pindah ke Kanada saat kami masih kecil.
Kami sangat menikmati menonton anime dan kartun dan bermimpi menjadi pengisi suara. Sayangnya, Jepang memiliki lingkungan yang sangat kompetitif di antara para seiyuu. Namun, tim pengisi suara kami dalam bahasa Inggris menyediakan terjemahan anime untuk berbagai negara, dan Anda dapat mendengarkan suara kami di berbagai anime.
Saat ini kami menyediakan layanan sulih suara untuk manga dan komik, dan kami mengharapkan dukungan Anda.

Rata-rata, kami menghabiskan sekitar 14 jam untuk membuat satu video.
Pada tahap menemukan ide, kami sudah mulai membuat sketsa naskah untuk menghemat waktu. Pada saat yang sama, kami mencari penulis dan seniman komik yang menggambar manga. Setelah berkomunikasi dengan mereka, kami membuat judul untuk video dan membuat sketsa pratinjau. Saat ini, kami telah menghabiskan sekitar 4 jam, karena pada kenyataannya ini adalah proses yang sangat panjang dan membosankan, tetapi sangat menyenangkan. Terkadang saya melakukannya sendiri, tetapi terkadang membutuhkan waktu sekitar 6 jam (tetapi ini jarang terjadi).
Kemudian kami menetapkan peran. Biasanya Shizuka menyelesaikan naskah yang telah kami sketsa di awal. Dia terus-menerus menonton berbagai tutorial dan mencari referensi agar komik aslinya memiliki makna yang berbeda. Dia suka mengulang makna keseluruhan cerita, biasanya dengan cara yang lucu.
Saat ini, saya sedang menggambar ulang sebagian besar komik, sesuai dengan naskah yang telah direvisi, sehingga komik tersebut pada akhirnya memiliki makna yang sama sekali berbeda. Saya juga menghabiskan banyak waktu untuk menggambar ulang pakaian karakter dan lingkungan sekitar. Sambil menggambar, saya harus menonton banyak tutorial dengan konten yang berbeda, karena menggambar adalah tugas yang agak rumit. Saya perlu menonton video tutorial di YouTube setiap saat tentang pembuatan storyboard, cara menggambar pakaian yang benar, anatomi manusia (terkadang hewan), dan pencahayaan, karena bayangan akan membuat gambar lebih baik. Kita perlu melihat banyak referensi untuk memilih ide pakaian, desain interior, dan hanya perlu mengarsir bayangan dalam pencahayaan tertentu. Saya selalu membuka semua kombinasi warna di monitor kedua. Dan sementara Shizuka menyelesaikan naskah, saya sedang mempersiapkan thumbnail untuk video tersebut. Di akhir, saya menambahkan dialog dari naskah Shizuka. Proses ini biasanya memakan waktu sekitar 6-8 jam. Saya tidak tahu berapa lama saya bisa menyelesaikannya sendiri tanpa bantuan Shizuka (Mungkin 16 jam?).
Setelah semua yang kami lakukan, kami mulai mengisi suara komik yang telah dibuat ulang. Karena kami adalah pengisi suara profesional dan telah lama berkecimpung di dunia akting suara, kami jarang membuat kesalahan. Saat mengedit video, kami sering kali harus mengisi ulang beberapa baris, karena mungkin ada kesalahan intonasi. Selanjutnya, saya mengedit bagian visual komik di Sony Vegas Pro 11, dan Shizuka mencari musik dari pustaka YouTube dan membuat trek audio di Ableton Live 11. Setelah kami menggabungkan semua upaya kami menjadi satu proyek, kami menekan tombol render. Saat itu kami telah menghabiskan waktu antara 13 dan 15 jam.
Setelah semua hal di atas, Anda dapat melihat video ini.
Terima kasih telah mendukung kami, menyukai, dan berlangganan kanal ini :)

Video ini dibuat hanya untuk tujuan hiburan dan humor dan tidak dimaksudkan untuk menyinggung siapa pun!
Semua materi di kanal ini telah diedit oleh Saikorin. Kami bukan pencipta aslinya, dan saya tidak mengambil kredit atas materi yang digunakan dalam video ini.
Semua materi telah dimodifikasi secara signifikan sesuai dengan aturan penggunaan wajar dan ditambahkan ke alur umum video.

"Penafian Hak Cipta Berdasarkan Pasal 107 Undang-Undang Hak Cipta 1976,

en-US.title: Veeronica X Guest 666 „ÄéComic Dub„Äè
en-US.description:
Veeronica X Guest 666 „ÄéComic Dub„Äè
üñ§ Honey, please subscribe :3
üîî Turn on notifications so you don't miss new videos!

Artist: Me (Rick)
Reference: koi 567, qemars, saikorin

Voice Actor: Me (Rick)
Voice Actress: Shuzuka

Producer: Saikorin
Twitter(X): https://x.com/Saikorin_
Discord(Not Skype): https://discord.gg/B3kfrVmWBR
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/SaikorinOfficial

Dear viewers, you are greeted by part of the team of professional voice acting for anime, films, comics, manga, manhwa and the rest.

Shuzuka and I moved to Canada when we were children.
We really enjoyed watching anime and cartoons and dreamed of becoming voice actors. Unfortunately, Japan has a very competitive environment among seiyuus. But our voices in English provide translations of anime for different countries, you could hear our voices in a variety of anime.
We are currently providing voice-over services for manga and comics, and hope for your support.

On average, we spend about 14 hours creating one video.
At the stage of coming up with an idea, we already begin to sketch out a script in order to save time. At the same time, we are looking for comic book authors and artists who draw manga. After communicating with them, we come up with a title for the video and sketch out a preview. By this point, we have already spent about 4 hours of our time, because in reality this is a very long and tedious process, but very fun. Sometimes I do it alone, but then it takes me about 6 hours (but this is rare).
Then we assign roles. Usually Shizuka completes the script that we sketched out at the beginning. She constantly watches various tutorials and looks for references so that the original comic has a different meaning. She likes to remake the meaning of the entire story, usually in a humorous way.
At this time, I am redrawing most of the comic, according to the redone script, so that the comic ultimately comes out with a completely different meaning. I also spend a huge part of my time redrawing the clothes on the characters and drawing the environment. While drawing, I have to watch a lot of tutorials of different content, since drawing is a rather complicated task. I need to watch instructional videos on YouTube all the time about storyboarding, how to properly draw clothes, human anatomy (sometimes animals) and lighting, as shadows make the drawing better. You need to look through a lot of references in order to choose an idea for clothing, interior design, and simply shading shadows in certain lighting. I absolutely always have all color combinations open on the second monitor. And while Shizuka is finishing the script, I‚Äôm preparing a thumbnail for the video. At the end I add dialogue from Shizuka's script. This usually takes us about 6-8 hours. I don't know how much I would have done it alone without Shizuka's help (Maybe 16 hours?).
After everything we've done, we start dubbing the remade comic. Since we are professional voice actors and have been doing voice acting for quite a long time, we make few mistakes. When editing a video, we often have to re-voice some lines, as we may make a mistake with the intonation. Next, I edit the visual part of the comic in Sony Vegas Pro 11, and Shizuka searches for music from the YouTube library and creates an audio track in Ableton Live 11. After we combine our efforts into one project, we press the render button. By this time we had already spent between 13 and 15 hours.
After all of the above, you were able to see this video.
Thank you for supporting us, liking and subscribing to the channel :)

This video was created for entertainment and humorous purposes only and is not intended to offend anyone!
All materials on this channel has been edited by Saikorin.
We are not the author of the original, I do not take credit for the materials that were used in this video.
All materials have been significantly modified in accordance with the rules of fair use and added to the general plot of the video.

Ian Munsick - Prairie Lament [Official Music Video]

Follow Ian:
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/ianmunsick/
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/ianmunsick/
Twitter - https://twitter.com/IanMunsick
Tiktok - https://www.tiktok.com/@ianmunsick

A native son of Wyoming, Ian Munsick accumulated over 1 billion global streams across just two albums ‚Äì¬†Coyote Cry¬†and¬†White Buffalo¬†‚Äì and a host of accolades, including 19 awards and 14 festival selections for his documentary,¬†White Buffalo: Voices of the West. Having painted a stampeding, spirited portrait of the American West with his sophomore album¬†White Buffalo¬†in 2023, Munsick is expanding on the concepts of the land, people, culture and stories that inspire him, on his most recent 20-track album,¬†Eagle Feather, released on April 18, 2025. In addition to selling over 100,000 headlining tickets in 2024, Munsick also opened on select dates of Lainey Wilson‚Äôs¬†Country‚Äôs Cool Again Tour¬†and supported Morgan Wallen on select dates of his record-setting¬†One Night At A Time Tour.¬†Munsick concluded his spring¬†Horses Are Faster Tour¬†in Nashville.¬†He has been named an ‚ÄúArtist to Watch‚Äù by Spotify, CMT, Fender,¬†MusicRow¬†and most recently was named a Martin Showcase Artist. Standout duet ‚ÄúLong Live Cowgirls‚Äù (with Cody Johnson) off of¬†White Buffalo¬†hit No. 1 on SiriusXM‚Äôs¬†The Highway¬†Hot 30 Countdown, was named one of Amazon Music‚Äôs Best Country Songs of 2022 and recently received RIAA Gold-certification alongside ‚ÄúLong Haul‚Äù and ‚ÄúHorses Are Faster.‚Äù Fans of Ian Munsick will always find an open heart, natural awe and plainspoken honesty as he rides on‚Ä¶ bringing the West to the rest. Online at¬†IanMunsick.com

#IanMunsick  #PrairieLament

snippet.title: The (Somewhat) Complete Lore of Silksong
snippet.description:
Gaming changed forever 2 months ago when Hollow Knight Silksong was finally released to the masses. But now that we've all completed it 100%, what was Silksong even about? In this video, we'll be diving deep into the lore of Hollow Knight: Silksong. And who knows, we just might learn a thing or two about ourselves in the process.

If you want to watch this video on a livestream with your audience, go right ahead! I don't mind.

Check out the Hollow Knight wiki here:
https://hollowknight.wiki

Check out my Discord server, mossbag & friends!
https://discord.gg/mossbag

Please follow me on Twitter. I equate my self worth to my follower count:
https://twitter.com/mossbag69

Too cool for Twitter? Fine, here's my Bluesky:
https://bsky.app/profile/mossbag.bsky.social

Link to script/list of songs/mods used:
https://mossbag.com/the-somewhat-complete-lore-of-silksong/

Translate this video into another language using Amara:
https://amara.org/videos/45fgAKyj055Y/info/the-somewhat-complete-lore-of-silksong

Video Chapters:
00:00 Intro
01:42 Promise of the Citadel
07:33 Cruelty of the Citadel
14:41 Truth of the Citadel
20:09 First Sinner
24:07 Waning of the Weavers
30:31 Citadel Caste
36:56 Cogwork Core
39:33 The Haunting
43:30 Silk-spun Children
46:00 Hunting down the Weavers
53:14 Events of Act 1
56:35 Events of Act 2
59:00 Weaver Queen Ending
1:00:36 Twisted Child Ending
1:01:47 Cut Ending (Strung to Serve)
1:02:37 Snared Silk Ending
1:04:46 Events of Act 3
1:15:00 Sister of the Void Ending
1:16:50 Outro

snippet.description:
Official Music Video for ‚ÄúI Sit In Parks" by Kelsea Ballerini.

Pre-order the upcoming EP, Mount Pleasant, now: https://orcd.co/kbmountpleasant

TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@kelseaballerini
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/kelseaballerini
Twitter: https://x.com/kelseaballerini

LYRICS:
I sit in parks 
It breaks my heart ‚Äòcause I see just how far I am
From the things that I want

Dad brought the picnic
Mom brought the sunscreen
Two kids are laughing and crying on red swings
We look about the same age
But we don‚Äôt have same Saturdays

Did I miss it
By now is it 
A lucid dream, is it my fault
For chasing things a body clock 
Doesn‚Äôt wait for
I did the damn tour
It‚Äôs what I wanted, what I got
I spun around and then I stopped
And wonder if I missed the mark

So, I sit in parks
Sunglasses dark and I 
Hit the vape, hallucinate a nursery with Noah‚Äôs Ark
They lay on a blanket
And God damn it, he loves her
I wonder if she wants my freedom
Like I want to be a mother

But Rolling Stone says I‚Äôm on the right road
So, I refill my Lexapro
Thinking

Did I miss it
By now is it 
A lucid dream, is it my fault
For chasing things a body clock 
Doesn‚Äôt wait for
I did the damn tour
It‚Äôs what I wanted, what I got
I spun around and then I stopped
And wonder if I missed the mark

So, I sit in parks
Checking benchmarks
Tarryn‚Äôs due in June
The album‚Äôs due in March

snippet.description:
Amanda The Adventurer 3 Full Gameplay is the FINAL GAME in the series -- Will we finally help Rebecca escape Hameln's evil laboratory?!
üçú SUBSCRIBE - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChd1FPXykD4pust3ljzq6hQ?sub_confirmation=1
üëâ BECOME A MEMBER - https://www.youtube.com/thinknoodles/join

ü§ñ Discord: https://discord.gg/thinknoodles

In Amanda the Adventurer 3, continue Riley Park‚Äôs journey, immediately following the events of the previous game, as they discover the truth behind the ongoing mysteries surrounding Amanda and Hameln.

After being left a mysterious tape by their Aunt Kate that set into motion a series of events surrounding the children‚Äôs show Amanda the Adventurer, Riley Park survived their Aunt‚Äôs attic only to find more mysteries and danger awaiting at the Kensdale Public Library. With the help of a mysterious masked woman, Riley barely escaped the library with their life, and now must explore the abandoned Hameln facilities.

In the final game, play through a return to form taking the best elements of both previous games to create an experience that is bound to thrill both returning and new players alike.

Bring closure to the story of Amanda, Riley, Aunt Kate, and everyone affected by the sinister production of Amanda the Adventurer and the Hameln Corporation‚Äôs mysterious motivations.

Get ready for one last adventure!

Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. snippet.title: The Insane All Perk Streak of 2025
snippet.description:
The All Perk Streak is my favorite challenge in DBD and this year winning with all 41 Killers turned out to be harder than ever before!

0:00:00 What is the All Perk Streak?
0:03:36 Trapper against all odds (Lery's)
0:13:46 Add-on Restrictions Explained
0:15:24 Chucky nerfed but not defeated (Suffocation Pit)
0:25:30 Nemesis needs a drink (Saloon)
0:37:24 The Many Issues of APS 2025
0:38:47 Least Obvious Stream Sniper of All Time
0:42:12 Split Queues & Event Modes
0:43:14 Wraith sweats his bells off (Groaning Storehouse)
0:58:47 Freddy has to clutch (Ormond Lake Mine)
1:09:38 The Plague Incident
1:10:18 Knight tunnels everyone (RPD West)
1:23:58 The Plague Incident (Again)
1:28:26 Houndmaster Final Match (Nostromo Wreckage)
1:38:23 Final Thoughts

All 41 matches VOD: https://youtu.be/MViTvWnberA
Playlist of All APS streams: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLw1u0_rvaca3I7k0cs5ie0sExJ8ykKZqM&si=s1ifWxWd4Hdeoato
